      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANNIE'S REGRET (3) continued her winning form with another strong run after leading them home making it three on end at this track over 425m (23.96). In sparkling form and expected to measure up again. DESPICABLE ANDY (1) missed the frame last time when seventh (26.43) at Warragul but prior to that had three placings in a row. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Some good form is emerging from his last run. One of the better chances. GOOSEBUMPS RICO (8) was in the minor money with a useful 24.06, finishing second in a Special conditions H at this track last start. Has the ability and can measure up. CHILL OUT PLATE (2) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
